#透過scoreboard story(dummy) + schedule 指令運行整個劇情
#The story is executed through the global function of the "story" scoreboard and the schedule control interval.

#偵測 story(dummy) 的 orantes(虛擬玩家名稱) 記分板是否為20 是的話改成19
#Detect whether the orantes (global) scoreboard of story(dummy) is 20, if so, change it to 19
execute if score orantes story matches 5 positioned -359 -57 -432 in game_map:orantes run effect clear @a[distance=..30]
execute if score orantes story matches 5 run scoreboard players set orantes story 6

